            information by contacting us.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mt-20">Cookie Policy:</h1>
          <p class="capitalize mt-4 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
            Our cookie policy explains how we use cookies and other tracking
            technologies on our website. We use cookies to provide a better user
