          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mt-20">
            Certificate of Incorporation:
          </h1>
          <p class="capitalize mt-4 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
            we have meticulously adhered to all legal requirements and
            regulations to ensure compliance and transparency. Our Certificate
            of Incorporation serves as evidence of our dedication to operating
            in a responsible and accountable manner.
            <br /><br />
